rs\", \"from\": 366, \"to\": 372}, {\"ngram\": \"event\", \"from\": 374, \"to\": 379}, {\"ngram\": \"updates\", \"from\": 384, \"to\": 391}, {\"ngram\": \"Evening Standard\", \"from\": 397, \"to\": 413}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourprivacy notice.\", \"from\": 419, \"to\": 442, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ourprivacy notice\", \"from\": 424, \"to\": 441}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are now just days away from theParisOlympics- the first in Europe since London 2012.\", \"from\": 444, \"to\": 531, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 519, \"end\": 530, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999979486347, \"rank\": 2.0511609908625015e-09, \"text\": \"London 2012\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"theParisOlympics-\", \"from\": 475, \"to\": 492}, {\"ngram\": \"Europe\", \"from\": 506, \"to\": 512}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How the world has changed since then.\", \"from\": 532, \"to\": 569, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 536, \"to\": 545}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This will be my 10th Games - twice as a competitor and eight times as a sports administrator.\", \"from\": 571, \"to\": 664, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my 10th Games\", \"from\": 584, \"to\": 597}, {\"ngram\": \"a competitor\", \"from\": 609, \"to\": 621}, {\"ngram\": \"eight times\", \"from\": 626, \"to\": 637}, {\"ngram\": \"a sports administrator\", \"from\": 641, \"to\": 663}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Often the build-up is challenging - and then the magic starts.\", \"from\": 665, \"to\": 727, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the build-up\", \"from\": 671, \"to\": 683}, {\"ngram\": \"the magic\", \"from\": 710, \"to\": 719}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We all fall in love with the Olympics again.\", \"from\": 728, \"to\": 772, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"love\", \"from\": 743, \"to\": 747}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 753, \"to\": 765}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Track and field athletics is often at the heart of this spectacle.\", \"from\": 774, \"to\": 840, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Track and field athletics\", \"from\": 774, \"to\": 799}, {\"ngram\": \"the heart\", \"from\": 812, \"to\": 821}, {\"ngram\": \"this spectacle\", \"from\": 825, \"to\": 839}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And the British team we are sending to France has some great stars -Keely Hodgkinson,Dina Asher-Smith,Josh Kerr,Molly Caudery,Matt Hudson-Smithand many, many more who can become national heroes in the next few weeks.\", \"from\": 841, \"to\": 1057, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 849, \"end\": 856, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9964582907302757, \"rank\": 0.003288375897089047, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 880, \"end\": 886, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.8181924527615821, \"rank\": 0.21777731650004878, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 909, \"end\": 925, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Keely Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\"}, {\"begin\": 926, \"end\": 942, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dina_Asher-Smith\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dina Asher-Smith\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dina_Asher-Smith\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dina_Asher-Smith\"}, {\"begin\": 943, \"end\": 947, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"score\": 0.9999999965734787, \"rank\": 3.07781673699115e-09, \"text\": \"Josh\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\"}, {\"begin\": 953, \"end\": 966, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Molly_Caudery\", \"score\": 0.999995872758395, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Molly Caudery\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Molly_Caudery\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Molly_Caudery\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some great stars\", \"from\": 891, \"to\": 907}, {\"ngram\": \"Matt Hudson-Smithand\", \"from\": 967, \"to\": 987}, {\"ngram\": \"national heroes\", \"from\": 1019, \"to\": 1034}, {\"ngram\": \"the next few weeks\", \"from\": 1038, \"to\": 1056}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Athletics is compellingbecause it is the original Olympic sport.\", \"from\": 1059, \"to\": 1123, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Athletics\", \"from\": 1059, \"to\": 1068}, {\"ngram\": \"compellingbecause\", \"from\": 1072, \"to\": 1089}, {\"ngram\": \"the original Olympic sport\", \"from\": 1096, \"to\": 1122}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At heart it remains gloriously simple and utterly accessible.\", \"from\": 1124, \"to\": 1185, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"heart\", \"from\": 1127, \"to\": 1132}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Today you can still turn up at an athletics track and chase your dreams regardless of your background.\", \"from\": 1186, \"to\": 1288, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an athletics track\", \"from\": 1217, \"to\": 1235}, {\"ngram\": \"your dreams\", \"from\": 1246, \"to\": 1257}, {\"ngram\": \"your background\", \"from\": 1272, \"to\": 1287}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The recent Daley Thompson documentary showed how the sport enabled one of our greatest Olympians to do this in the Eighties.\", \"from\": 1289, \"to\": 1413, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1300, \"end\": 1314, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daley_Thompson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Daley Thompson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daley_Thompson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daley_Thompson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 1338, \"to\": 1347}, {\"ngram\": \"our greatest Olympians\", \"from\": 1363, \"to\": 1385}, {\"ngram\": \"the Eighties\", \"from\": 1400, \"to\": 1412}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That story is repeated day in, day out at athletics clubs around Britain.\", \"from\": 1414, \"to\": 1487, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1479, \"end\": 1486, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9995342042545367, \"rank\": 0.00046542124998714767, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That story\", \"from\": 1414, \"to\": 1424}, {\"ngram\": \"repeated day\", \"from\": 1428, \"to\": 1440}, {\"ngram\": \"athletics clubs\", \"from\": 1456, \"to\": 1471}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am proud that kids watching our athletes during the Olympics and then the Paralympics a couple of weeks later will see themselves reflected back It is also one of the country's most diverse sports with athletes drawn from every kind of community and background.\", \"from\": 1489, \"to\": 1755, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"kids\", \"from\": 1505, \"to\": 1509}, {\"ngram\": \"our athletes\", \"from\": 1519, \"to\": 1531}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1539, \"to\": 1551}, {\"ngram\": \"then the Paralympics\", \"from\": 1556, \"to\": 1576}, {\"ngram\": \"a couple\", \"from\": 1577, \"to\": 1585}, {\"ngram\": \"weeks\", \"from\": 1589, \"to\": 1594}, {\"ngram\": \"the country's most diverse sports\", \"from\": 1654, \"to\": 1687}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1693, \"to\": 1701}, {\"ngram\": \"every kind\", \"from\": 1713, \"to\": 1723}, {\"ngram\": \"community\", \"from\": 1727, \"to\": 1736}, {\"ngram\": \"background\", \"from\": 1741, \"to\": 1751}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ahead of the heart-breakingEuro 2024 finalagainst Spain, Labour's new Culture Secretary Lisa Nandy said the England men's team looked, sounded and felt like modern Britain.\", \"from\": 1756, \"to\": 1928, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1806, \"end\": 1811, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9665118019385818, \"rank\": 0.03459238758270272, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1813, \"end\": 1819, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Labor_Party\", \"score\": 0.6920208651401631, \"rank\": 0.40479140123470336, \"text\": \"Labour\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Labor_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Labor_Party\"}, {\"begin\": 1826, \"end\": 1843, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Secretary_of_State_for_Digital,_Culture,_Media_and_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9999974052986556, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Culture Secretary\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Secretary_of_State_for_Digital,_Culture,_Media_and_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Secretary_of_State_for_Digital,_Culture,_Media_and_Sport\"}, {\"begin\": 1844, \"end\": 1854, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lisa_Nandy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lisa Nandy\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resourc